  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Crusade Fleet Quintus is desperate for a victory when the Ultramarines cruiser Ithraca's Vengeance becomes trapped in a becalmed system inside the Pariah Nexus. Captain Aeschelus and Lieutenants Nemetus and Praxamedes face a Necron technology-grid that drains souls for the Silent Kingdom, while Overlord Simut, Plasmancer Ah-hotep and Skorpekh Lord Zozar press their own fractured agenda. What begins as a crusade rescue turns into a choice with no clean honor: die trying to break the Nexus, or abandon the sector so Guilliman can be warned. A 9th-edition on-ramp built as last-stand war-story, Necron mystery and new-era primer.",
